title: Game of Thrones - Seasons 1 - 3 English Subs 720p
description:
Game of Thrones 

Seasons 1 - 3

720p

File video format is MP4
Audio is 2 channel stereo

English Subtitle srt files included for each episode.


I wanted to watch the first three seasons with a friend that never seen the show before, and I also wanted to get ready for season 4 to start.  

These were the best rips that I could find, so I put them all together, and also found English subtitle files for Dothraki language.
